1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,910
[Episode 58]

2
00:00:04,410 --> 00:00:05,940
I really don't understand.

3
00:00:06,490 --> 00:00:12,090
I've done everything possible
Pestering him, even offering physical comfort.

4
00:00:13,770 --> 00:00:20,890
Apologizing
Begging for another chance.

5
00:00:23,330 --> 00:00:25,490
But why
Won't Bin talk to me?

6
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:30,210
Am I missing something?

7
00:00:33,210 --> 00:00:36,050
Are you talking to me
Or just thinking out loud?

8
00:00:37,850 --> 00:00:40,850
I'll talk to anyone
I have nobody left.

9
00:00:43,570 --> 00:00:45,170
Can you answer me then?

10
00:00:46,930 --> 00:00:47,810
No.

11
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,610
But I think
Someone can answer your question.

12
00:00:54,690 --> 00:00:55,370
Who?

13
00:01:23,610 --> 00:01:26,490
Why did you
Give up so easily today?

14
00:01:31,370 --> 00:01:33,630
I didn't want to make Bin uncomfortable.

15
00:01:33,770 --> 00:01:40,770
Even today, I still don't know
Why Bin is avoiding me.

16
00:01:44,770 --> 00:01:53,530
I know you love Bin
And you've been trying to steal him from me.

17
00:01:54,490 --> 00:02:02,010
Let me ask you seriously. When Bin was
With me, weren't you jealous?

18
00:02:07,810 --> 00:02:15,930
I was, but Bin said
He likes people who care about him.

19
00:02:15,930 --> 00:02:21,450
Not those who possess him
I didn't understand at first.

20
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:26,410
But seeing your face
I completely understand now.

21
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:30,290
Because you're just selfish.

22
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:37,370
Someone who controls others
Wanting everything your way.

23
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:43,570
But not everything
Will go as you wish.

24
00:02:45,410 --> 00:02:51,610
Because I
Don't need to possess Bin.

25
00:02:52,770 --> 00:03:00,330
As long as he's happy
That's enough for me.

26
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:14,550
You should ask yourself
What your so-called love really is.

27
00:03:16,370 --> 00:03:17,730
Would Bin ever like you?

28
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:35,110
[To Be Continued]
